1.title: Swing Into Action: Part 1
1.plot: Yuya Sakaki aims to become an "Entertainment Duelist". He practices dueling every day alongside his childhood friend, Yuzu. One day, he receives a challenge for an exhibition match from the Pro Duelist, "Strong Ishijima". Although Yuya excitedly fends off his attacks in their Action Duel, he's eventually pushed into a corner.

2.title: Swing Into Action: Part 2
2.plot: Yuya tries out his new "Pendulum Summon".

3.title: Trade Bait: Part 1
3.plot: It could be curtains for Yuya when a rival student cons him out of his Pendulum Cards!

4.title: Trade Bait: Part 2
4.plot: Still shocked by Sylvio's Pendulum Summon, Yuya must find his focus if he wants to save his friends from a 100-story drop!

5.title: Toying Around: Part 1
5.plot: The new kid in town drives Yuya bananas when he begs Yuya to be his duel teacher! Unfortunately for Yuya, this blue-haired battler won't give up until Yuya gives in!

6.title: Toying Around: Part 2
6.plot: Yuya's getting schooled by his wannabe student, Sora! Can Yuya turn things around and teach Sora a lesson about winning, or is Yuya's Pendulum power not going to make the grade?

7.title: Mr. Mystery
7.plot: Still steaming from his loss to Yuya, Sylvio looks to get some payback! But when Zuzu steps in to stop his plans, a mysterious stranger comes out of the shadows to show her how it's done!

8.title: Bad Business
8.plot: The Leo Institute is looking to take over Yuya's duel school, and they're bringing 3 of their most dangerous duelists to take down whoever dares stand in their way!

9.title: Dueling with the Stars
9.plot: The battle to save Yuya's duel school goes galactic when Yuya faces off against Leo Institute's Dipper, an out-of-this-world duelist whose interstellar skills could have Yuya seeing stars!

10.title: You Show 'Em
10.plot: It's a gem of a duel when Zuzu faces a fierce Fusion Summoner whose jewel monsters are a cut above the rest! Can Zuzu and her Divas belt out a victory, or will the Leo Institute's diamond of a duelist force a final face-off?

11.title: Going, Going, Gong
11.plot: It's all up to Gong to save You Show from falling into the hands of the Leo Institute! Can Gong stare down defeat without moving his feet, or will a sword-swinging Syncro Summoner slice and dice his way to victory?

12.title: Battle Under the Big Top
12.plot: It's a battle under the big top, but no one's clowning around! Yuya duels Declan to determine the fate of Yuya's duel school!

13.title: Circus Surprise!
13.plot: Declan has a surprise in store that could swing the duel his way! Can Yuya take down the best the Leo Institute has to offer, or will Declan's deck prove to be unbeatable?

14.title: The Show Must Go On
14.plot: Yuya's down in the dumps, but Principal Boyle's not having it! Looking to snap Yuya out of his funk, Skip challenges Yuya to a duel to prove that the show must go on!

15.title: In It to Win It
15.plot: Still stinging from her defeat against the Leo Institute, Zuzu turns to an unlikely source for some assistance - Sora! But before her training can commence, a familiar looking stranger shows up, putting her lesson on hold!

16.title: Menu Venue: Part 1
16.plot: To gain eligibility to join the Junior Youth Championship, Yuya has to win 4 official duels consecutively. He ends up dueling is Michio Mokota, a cuisine Duelist with high popularity among the housewives.

17.title: Menu Venue: Part 2
17.plot: Yuya faces a ferocious attack against Michio Mokota's Cooking Duel.

18.title: Trapped in a Card
18.plot: It's a case of mistaken identity when Yuya is eyed as the primary suspect for attacking Leo students! But when Yuya crosses paths with the real culprit, things go from bad to worse!

19.title: Quiz Quagmire: Part 1
19.plot: Yuya matches minds with the quiz whiz extraordinaire Pierre L'Supérieure in a duel of wits! Can Yuya outsmart the smartest boy on Earth, or will Yuya end up scratching his head in defeat?

20.title: Quiz Quagmire: Part 2
20.plot: In the finale of the mind-bending match that's part-duel, part-quiz show - one wrong answer could mean curtains for Yuya! Can he outduel and outthink a trivia whiz who's never wrong?

21.title: Beyond Belief
21.plot: Duelists throughout the city are continuously being attacked, and everyone is on the search to find out the who, how and why!

22.title: A Date with Fate: Part 1
22.plot: Yuya's future takes a terrifying turn for the worse when he battles a fortunetelling foe who predicts this will be his last duel ever! Can Yuya fix his fate and avoid a devastating disaster, or has his luck finally run out?

23.title: A Date with Fate: Part 2
23.plot: As Yuya's battle against the fortunetelling predictress Aura flares to its finish, it becomes crystal clear that Yuya's danger-filled future is becoming a reality!

24.title: For Our Tomorrows
24.plot: Mysteries are revealed when the masked duelist who's been terrorizing Leo Institute students is confronted and challenged to a battle royal!

25.title: Battle Between Buddies: Part 1
25.plot: Yuya needs one more win to get into the Championship, but it will be his most difficult battle yet when he discovers he has to beat his best bud Gong in order to move on!

26.title: Battle Between Buddies: Part 2
26.plot: The battle between best buds Yuya and Gong for a spot in the Arc League Championships rages to a friend-zied finish!

27.title: Challengers Assemble
27.plot: Let the games begin! The top duelists from around the globe have gathered together for the Arc League Championships to find out who's the best duelist in the world!

28.title: Something's Fishy
28.plot: Allie is looking to make a big splash at the Arc League Championship, but she soon finds herself in over her head! Can Allie's deck of fishy friends turn the tides, or will her mysterious opponent sink her chances of winning?

29.title: Fusion Foes
29.plot: Zuzu takes center stage in an epic rematch against Leo Institute's dueling diamond, Julia Krystal! Will Zuzu avenge her earlier loss and walk away a winner, or will history repeat itself and leave Zuzu singing the blues?

30.title: Gong the Strong
30.plot: When Gong's old sparring partner sets a trap for Yuya, the only way Gong can save his friend is to forfeit his duel and get tossed from the tourney!

31.title: The Pendulum Swings Both Ways: Part 1
31.plot: Sylvio finally has just the thing to take Yuya down - a deck full of Pendulum Cards! Could Yuya's days in the spotlight be done for?

32.title: The Pendulum Swings Both Ways: Part 2
32.plot: Yuya is off his game and on the run as Sylvio zeroes in on zeroing out his life points! If Yuya can't get into the swing of things, this could be his final performance!

33.title: Making the Cut: Part 1
33.plot: Sora is psyched to put on a showstopping duel for the fans, but his opponent Shay is set to turn Sora's one man show into a no man show!

34.title: Making the Cut: Part 2
34.plot: Sora and Shay's heated duel hits its boiling point when dark secrets about their hidden history come to light! Could there be something sinister behind Sora's sweet-toothed smile?

35.title: Sora's Secrets: Part 1
35.plot: While Yuto is looking for answers, Sora is looking to get some revenge! But when these two tangle, Yuya finds out more than he ever expected!

36.title: Sora's Secrets: Part 2
36.plot: Surprises are in the cards as the battle between Sora and Yuto comes to an unexpected conclusion! But just when Yuya thinks he's seen everything, a new face shows up on the scene that makes Yuya do a triple take!

37.title: A Dark Reflection
37.plot: Yuya can't believe his eyes when he finds himself standing face-to-face-to-face with two lookalikes who are out to destroy each other... and everything in sight!

38.title: Warped
38.plot: Yuya is in a coma, and nothing has been able to stir him from his terrifying state! Is Yuya down for the count, or will his duelmate's ESP and TLC make him A-OK?

39.title: Imperial Wrath Awakening
39.plot: Yuya's opponent is Isao Kachidoki from the Ryozanpaku School in the second round of the Maiami Championship.

40.title: Stealth Warriors
40.plot: When a mysterious visitor threatens to throw the Championship into chaos, Declan moves in to uncover who they are and soon finds himself facing off against a merciless mercenary!

41.title: Bracing for Battle
41.plot: Declan confronts Celina and shares a story from their past that reveals a frightening future!

42.title: Battle Fields
42.plot: It's time for a nail biting battle royal in the ARC League Championship! With four battle zones to choose from, the action has never been more mesmerizing or the duels more dangerous!

43.title: Fire and Ice
43.plot: While Yuya is looking to knock the competition out cold in the Volcano Zone, the Iceberg Zone is heating up as Zuzu and Gong team up to defrost their foes!

44.title: Danger Zones
44.plot: As the battle royal rumbles on, Yuya finds himself caught in the crossfire when he stumbles across a battle between not-so-noble Knights!

45.title: Obelisk Assault
45.plot: Yuya takes on a terrifying trio from Fusion Dimension who turn their victims into cards!

46.title: Dragon's Vengeance
46.plot: Outnumbered, outmatched, and out of options, will Yuya tap into a deep-seeded darkness to overcome defeat?

47.title: Identity Crisis
47.plot: Zuzu races to stay one step ahead of a cold-blooded hunter who's hot on her heels! Can Zuzu ditch this danger, or will he prove too cunning for her to escape?

48.title: Battlefronts
48.plot: Sparks fly in the Volcano Zone when all our heroes face off against the full fury of Fusion Dimension's elite Obelisk Force! With more than life points on the line, the action has never been hotter!

49.title: Fighting for Fun
49.plot: Are friends now foes as Yuya and Sora go deck to deck in a fiery face-off?

1.title: Dueling Declan
1.plot: Furious by Declan's revealed plan about the "Lancers", Yuya challenges him to a duel.

2.title: Kings vs. Dragons
2.plot: Yuya's battle with Declan takes a turn for the worse when Declan's majestic monsters give Yuya the royal treatment!

3.title: Parental Guidance: Part 1
3.plot: It's a family feud when Yuya takes on his mom in a duel where there's more to lose than just his allowance! Can Yuya avoid being run down by Paradise City's most feared motorcycle momma?

4.title: Parental Guidance: Part 2
4.plot: The battle between Yuya and his mom kicks into high gear! Can Yuya avoid being grounded, or will Loco Yoko put the pedal to the metal and throttle her way to victory?

5.title: City 'Scape
5.plot: As Zuzu and Yugo try to unravel the riddle of Yuya's dimensional doubles, their sleuthing is cut short by Sector Security!

6.title: Tops Speed
6.plot: Zuzu and Yugo redline their Duel Runner in a high-stakes Turbo Duel with Sector Security! Can they outrun the long arm of the law, or will Security put the brakes on their escape?

56.title: Synchro Sector
56.plot: When Yuya and his pals arrive in the Synchro Dimension, Sector Security is waiting for them with open arms ... and cuffs! Can Yuya smooth things out before Sylvio and Celina put a wrinkle in his plan?

57.title: Super Duelists
57.plot: It's a superheroic showdown in the Synchro Dimension pitting Super Gong against his arch-nemesis, Dennis the Destroyer!

58.title: Invitation to the Dark Duel
58.plot: A mysterious and shady man named Gallager appeared before Gongenzaka and Dennis.

59.title: Dueling's Most Wanted
59.plot: Dennis deployed his Pendulum Summon in his Duel against Shun. Detecting that Summon, Roget, the Director of the Security, decided to keep an eye on them. On the other hand, Reira was depressed since Reiji is not with him. Yuya wants to make Reira smile, but a slight difference in their opinions caused some hostility between Crow and Yuya.

60.title: No Cards, No Pardon
60.plot: Yuya learns the ins and outs of The Facility the hard way by coming face-to-face with the toughest and most dangerous duelist in the cell block: the Kingpin!

imdb.plot outline: Thanks to the Leo Corporation, headed by Reiji Akaba, new advancements to Solid Vision, the holographic system that gives life to the Duel Monsters card game, give physical mass to monsters and environments, allowing players to interact directly with them. This has given birth to challenging Action Duels, in which duelists may traverse environments to locate Action Cards to help them in a pinch. The story follows Yuya Sakaki, a second year middle school student at Maiami City's You Show Duel School, whose father disappeared three years ago when he was scheduled for an important duel. While facing off against the current Action Duel champion, Yuya awakens a new power from his pendant, known as Pendulum Summoning.
